creator: XcelTrip LLC
descriptionHtml:
XcelTrip is a Next- Generation travel platform powered by the blockchain technology has been built solely to disrupt the ever-growing trillion-dollar travel industry. The features are scrupulously created to democratize digital asset use-cases, that challenges the monopoly of the ecosystem by giving the power back to the users by providing the users full control over their bookings and their anonymity.

● Over 1.5 Million Hotels Worldwide

We have curated some of the best hotels worldwide for you to choose from over 230+ countries around the world.

● Over 400 Airlines To Choose From

XcelTrip has over 400 airlines for you to choose from with any of the currency listed on the platform.

● Multi-Payment Option

XcelTrip allows you to choose from debit/credit card booking to leading digital assets like bitcoin, ethereum, litecoin, xceltoken plus (XLAB), dash, verge.

● 24/7 Customer Support

You can contact our customer service via live chat on the website, email or online ticketing system.

● App notifications

Get the best deals & offers

● Reward-Based System

Earn instant rewards on the XcelTrip app by booking your vacations, with our innovative tokenized incentive programs that include Smart discounts, referrals for invitations, loyalty programs and earn up-to 50% cash-back.

● Invite & Earn

Invite your friends/family and earn rewards.

● Property listing opportunity

List your hotels BNB & homestays. Get an opportunity to grow with XcelTrip.

● Bargain opportunity

Get a chance to bargain with your favorite hotels and save money on every bookings.

● Share & Earn Opportunity

Get an opportunity to earn on every hotel recommendations. You can share any hotels link to your multiple social media accounts and earn $0.01 in XLAB on every click hits. You can also earn 20% of the booking amount in XLAB if someone clicks on the link and makes a successful booking.

● Emergency SOS Service

Use In-app SOS service to track and notify about emergency situations. You can add up to 3 emergency contact person's email and phone numbers so they get instantly notified as soon as you hit the panic button.

● Become IMP & get unlimited income opportunity

Become our independent marketing partner (IMP), list any hotels property, and earn up to 20% on each bookings.
